title: Halloween Pumpkin icon 2016
body: hi i was just curious on when i will receive my icon for mystery gifting my friend for halloween. Will i be receiving it?

replies.body: We're still sending icons out for the Teemoing Event until **November 17th**, so it should be sometime between now and then. If you don't have it by then, [hit us up](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll help you out.
